</li>
<li>
<p>Companies Slowly Join Cloud-Computing，By&nbsp;<span>Brad Stone&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span>Ashlee Vance，https://www.nytimes.com/2010/04/19/technology/19cloud.html</span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
